{"tid":710994,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"廢中同事小撚器","createTime":"2018-06-21T07:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T03:19:42.000Z","uid":37516,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"77ac40c143d58425124435cf6baa7a5e69d9252b","tid":710994,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n公司有個廢中同事，初初黎個陣都覺得佢成日扮撚晒野架啦，叫佢做D簡單野又話唔識又話唔關佢事咁。<br />\n好啦做左成年鳩幾，日日見條撚樣坐係位捉下精靈，閒時又出去成粒鐘捉精靈咁，終於聽到佢話唔做，諗住一天都光晒啦，屌佢老味最後呢幾個星期，日日係到又放負又伊伊哦哦，呢幾日仲想屈我地請佢食飯咁，隔離team同事同佢同一日last day 見人地有人請食飯佢自己就係到自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話唔請佢食又乜又柒，平時又唔係成日一齊食飯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉，幾撚時先走呀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90f70f440d52bacd849f01c9b841e75bf60de82","tid":710994,"uid":95626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cc7fadfd951957590f57a660c92fda17d2a7bd","tid":710994,"uid":128057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"你條廢柴"},{"pid":"9fe9874e89d3d264b375b48e80ad83653148343c","tid":710994,"uid":22364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"公司都有個廢中好似樓主講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid